      <text>Comparative analysis of C-type lectin domain proteins in the ghost moth, Thitarodes xiaojinensis (Lepidoptera: Hepialidae).</text>
      <annotation id="17">
        <infon key="type">Gene</infon>
        <infon key="identifier"></infon>
        <infon key="annotator">5ef4bd7e0113</infon>
